ygData.messageBody:
Im on my way to Permafrost or Paw / splitpaw anytime this week.
There r stuff at Paw for my quest. Permafrost should be good huntin but it
damn cold and putting on extra clothes will add to me weight.
I have consider staying at Keeps for Pickclaws, but they hurt me bad and too
well camped for my blood.

I hope Trifrost come on-line this few days to show us around halas his
Hometown. That should help a bit.
YO ! Tri, Where u over the Weekend eh? MIA ? I know, I know GF. HEY RPG
gamer got no life and no GF ! remember ( AH, its good Im married)
Trifrost should Group with Ziltus , Ling and Flying Fox at HH pass. Man ,
Damn Wiz , Magician and Shaman will PISSED lotsa ppl there.. Kickass!

Entrenri should consider joining Ziltus at HH pass too.

Yiyang at HH pass..for now
